author: newsroom@capegazette.com (Staff)
title: Delaware Senior Olympics holds Racquetball Championship
text:
Delaware Senior Olympics holds Racquetball Championship Oct 08, 2015 Source: Submitted 
The Delaware Senior Olympics 2015 Racquetball Championship was held Sept. 26 on the courts of Midway Fitness. Midway Fitness has hosted this annual event for the past four years. Senior Olympics participants are ages 50 and over. 
Shown are the 2015 winners of the gold and silver medals (l-r) state organizer Michael Ohr, Aram Terzian, Ed Wilkowski, Tom Jones, Terri Rock, Jack Vaughan, Ingrid Callmann, Dan Nime, John Walker and Bob Burakiewicz. 
For more information about Delaware Senior Olympics, go to delawareseniorolympics.org .
